[^li13-1]: Institute of Museum and Library Services (IMLS), [_Public Libraries Survey._](https://www.imls.gov/research-evaluation/data-collection/public-libraries-survey) Annual. See also OverDrive's annual circulation reports and American Library Association (ALA) state-level return-on-investment studies.

